WITH "CTE_Cash_Discounts" AS (
    SELECT 
        "PayableItem"."ID"                          AS "ID",
        "PayableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate1"        AS "CashDiscountDueDate",
        "PayableItem"."CashDiscountEligibleAmount1" AS "CashDiscountEligibleAmount"
    FROM "o_custom_PayableItem" AS "PayableItem"
    WHERE "PayableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate1" IS NOT NULL
    UNION ALL 
    SELECT 
        "PayableItem"."ID"                          AS "ID",
        "PayableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate2"        AS "CashDiscountDueDate",
        "PayableItem"."CashDiscountEligibleAmount2" AS "CashDiscountEligibleAmount"
    FROM "o_custom_PayableItem" AS "PayableItem"
    WHERE "PayableItem"."CashDiscountDueDate2" IS NOT NULL
),
    "CTE_Disc_Level" AS (
    SELECT 
        "Cash_Discounts"."ID"                                               AS "ID",
        "Cash_Discounts"."CashDiscountDueDate"                              AS "CashDiscountDueDate",
        "Cash_Discounts"."CashDiscountEligibleAmount"                       AS "CashDiscountEligibleAmount",
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "Cash_Discounts"."ID"
        ORDER BY "Cash_Discounts"."CashDiscountDueDate")                    AS "DiscountTermOrder"
    FROM "CTE_Cash_Discounts" AS "Cash_Discounts"
)                        
SELECT 
    'PayableItemCashDiscountDueDate' || '::' || "Disc_Level"."ID" 
        || '::' || "Disc_Level"."DiscountTermOrder"                                            AS "ID",
    "Disc_Level"."ID"                                                                          AS "PayableItem",
    "Disc_Level"."CashDiscountDueDate"                                                         AS "Time",
    "Disc_Level"."DiscountTermOrder"                                                           AS "DiscountTermOrder",
    "Disc_Level"."CashDiscountEligibleAmount"                                                  AS "EligibleDiscountAmount"
FROM "CTE_Disc_Level" AS "Disc_Level"
WHERE "Disc_Level"."CashDiscountDueDate" IS NOT NULL
